Date Reviewed: 07/02/08 ged08 Member Since: 07/02/08
View Member's: Reviews Within 2 hours of payment I received a FedEx tracking number which gave detailed information of the packages progress. It arrived in the UK in 2.5 days as predicted. The Adobe Creative Suite package contained all 3 DVD's with extras and a Workflow book, I had no problems installing or registering with Adobe. This was the full retail product at a great price - and great service, Thanks ! Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 02/01/08 Iqmi74 Member Since: 02/01/08
View Member's: Reviews This was a company purchase of a large amount for both Adobe and Microsoft Office 2003 products. Having never having done business with Uktechstore before we were hesitant to go forward, we contacted them asking them few questions and some references, they replied in a swift manner with good credentials. We put the purchase through and just after 3 days we received our shipment just as described, 100% genuine and eveything installed and works just fine. We will now be using this company for our future purchases. With quick customer response, unbeatable pricing and genuine product, you cannot go wrong. We highly recommend Uktechstore for your software needs, these guys are able to deliver!! Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 20/09/07 DiFranks Member Since: 20/09/07
View Member's: Reviews Price for product was excellent. Had problems placing the order .. problem with my bank, not with UKtechstore. Emailed UKtechstore, they even telephoned me to assist in the order. Eventually my bank got their act together, and I was able to place the order early evening Tuesday and the product was delivered by midday Thursday. Their support email was excellent, quickly responding and very very helpful and friendly. Would certainly order again from them. Well done UKTechstore .... at last a company that cares! Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 31/08/07 pushhump Member Since: 31/08/07
View Member's: Reviews Don't buy from this company. Ordered on the 10th Aug, the company went on holdiay on the 11th Aug without sending my goods or informing me that they were going on holiday. I finally got a refund on the 31st Aug. They take ages to reply to emails and you can't contact them by telephone - avoid them!!! Retailer Response (06/09/07): We notified the client of the late shipment and the client agreed to wait, when we did not receive our inventory, we immediately notified the client and processed their refund. We were in contact with the client throughout our holiday period. We were cordial with the client and returned the full amount without question. This client review is unjust. Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 17/07/07 freddylotus Member Since: 17/07/07
View Member's: Reviews Customer service is excellent and they always strive to make sure that I'm happy. Software arrived as advertised and functioned fine. No problems with activation. I would and do order from them all the time. Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 18/06/07 purimanesh Member Since: 18/06/07
View Member's: Reviews Purchased Adobe Creative Suite Premium CS3 and product came in 3 business days, product exactly as described. Easy shopping, fast shipping and this was the best price I found online. Highly recommended! Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 24/03/07 wrebbit77 Member Since: 24/03/07
View Member's: Reviews Can't beat the pricing, speedy customer service and fast delivery. Will shop here again. 2 thumbs up :) Overall Rating
